Hong Kong Government to Appeal Maid Residency Ruling

-- B y   M a r c o   L u i
-- 
2011-09-30T08:15:18Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-30/hong-kong-government-to-appeal-maid-residency-ruling-correct-.html
(Corrects to remove date of appeal.)  The  Hong Kong  government plans to
appeal against a court ruling paving the way for foreign maids
to apply for permanent residency, Ambrose Lee, the secretary for
security, told reporters today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
